 and the market's skew towards long or short positions. Funding settles every hour, with rates dynamically adjusting based on open interest imbalances and oracle price deviations. The platform uses Chainlink price feeds for BLUR, ensuring funding rates reflect real market conditions across centralized exchanges."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
